=== Go/no-go recommendation ===
NO-GO on measuring Vulkan offload with the current Pixel 6 binaries.
Deferred: build llama.cpp with -DGGML_VULKAN=ON against Android NDK,
push the resulting llama-bench, then re-run the 3x sweep. No upstream
prebuilt asset to shortcut this.
